cmdline: sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install -y jq

curl -s http://172.18.0.5:8000/openapi.json | jq -r '
  .paths | to_entries[] | .key as $p
  | .value | to_entries[] | select(.key!="parameters")
  | "\(.key|ascii_upcase)  \($p)"' | sort

curl -s http://172.18.0.5:8000/openapi.json | jq -r '
  . as $d
  | def deref(s):
      if (s|type)=="object" and (s["$ref"]? | type)=="string"
      then $d.components.schemas[(s["$ref"]|split("/")|last)]
      else s end;
  def ptype(v):
      (deref(v)) as $v
      | if ($v.type? // "") != "" then $v.type
        elif ($v.items? // empty) then "array<" + (ptype($v.items)) + ">"
        else "object" end;

  ($d.paths["/ingest"].post.requestBody.content["application/json"].schema) as $s
  | (deref($s)) as $schema
  | "Required: " + ( ($schema.required // []) | join(", ") ),
    "Props:",
    ( ($schema.properties // {}) | to_entries[] | "  \(.key): " + ptype(.value) )
'
